    "body" : "Let me clarify: I <i>want to use it</i> because it usually is more readable in writing out above types of algorithms. I <i>expect it to be there</i> because it is more natural for the CPU. I will not make any assumptions as to what the JIT does or does not do, because assuming either way about compilers wil bite you."
