    "body" : "Java works on a higher abstraction level. Unless you can see the intrinsic methods use some specific opcodes, you can&#39;t assume anything. However, that doesn&#39;t mean the JVM wouldn&#39;t internally use <code>divmod</code> if JIT so chooses."
