      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "This is a great explanation of why it doesn&#39;t work today, but it doesn&#39;t preclude some version of the language in the far future supporting some syntax like <code>q = x &#47; y remainder r</code> as syntactic sugar for <code>q = x &#47; y; r = x % y</code> (and the JIT turning the latter into divmod)."
